<L>__{exterior camp night (moonlight)}
<A>__{long shot angles past horseman. the horseman, who has been approaching from the east, tops a rise and looks off at the camp. he is a shadowy figure in the palo dark. for a moment, as the fire still blazes, figures are visible in the camp. then the fire goes out. the horseman dismounts, pulling his rifle from his scabbard. moving to his horse's head he puts a hand on the animal's nostrils. he looks toward the camp for a moment then starts cautiously along the road.}
